{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849290/extras/Wishlist_EN.gif?t=1736239833\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Jeweler Simulator is a simulation game where you can manage a jewelry store, engage in buying and selling, and grow your business with the profits you make. It features fun mechanics and a detailed open world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game is filled with customers wanting to sell you their rings, necklaces, and ores. Test the authenticity of the items and assess their value.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you trade and keep your store clean, you\u2019ll earn the right to improve your skills. This will help you become a better jeweler over time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Purchase more luxurious furniture, master your profession, and raise your prestige. Let people be dazzled by your brilliance!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849290/extras/Line.png?t=1736239833\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849290/extras/Roadmap_EN.png?t=1736239833\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849290/extras/Line.png?t=1736239833\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849290/extras/GIF_Measure_EN.gif?t=1736239833\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849290/extras/GIF_Measure_02.gif?t=1736239833\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Before buying a product, it\u2019s important to check if it\u2019s real. You should look for damage on metals and see how they react to magnets. For stones, you need to check their color, clarity, carat, and cut carefully. Different mini-games will help you do these tests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849290/extras/Blank1.png?t=1736239833\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849290/extras/GIF_Sale_EN.gif?t=1736239833\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849290/extras/GIF_Sale_02.gif?t=1736239833\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can bargain with customers who want to sell you something or buy from you. There is also a variety of dialogues, so you can have different conversations with each customer. Some of these conversations are wicked.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849290/extras/Blank2.png?t=1736239833\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849290/extras/GIF_Decorate_EN.gif?t=1736239833\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849290/extras/GIF_Decorate_01.gif?t=1736239833\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With cool display cases, nice counters, and useful storage, you can make your shop look better. You can place the furniture how you like and store more items to sell at the same time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849290/extras/Line.png?t=1736239833\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849290/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=17362